rvation creates discrete categorical structure by terminating continuous evolution. This is irreversible—once a categorical state is completed, it cannot be re-entered. Measurement is not passive recording but active creation of discrete structure from continuous reality. Parameters: Generic wave function with multiple frequency components.}}{9}{figure.caption.3}\protected@file@percent }
